label: A7B3C3_hP26_186_3a4b_2ab_a2b-001
title: Al$_{7}$C$_{3}$N$_{3}$ Structure
comments:
(Jeffrey, 1963) place the structure in space group $P6_{3}mc$ \#186, but give the structure in a pseudo-hexagonal cell in space group $Cmc2_{1}$ \#36.  With the help of FINDSYM we converted this to the hexagonal structure. 
 (Jeffrey, 1966) uses the $P6_{3}mc$ space group exclusively, and we list the ICSD entry associated with that paper.
